OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772644277
OL,3,CSpurs becomes first English football
OL,4,Cclub to add audio descriptions to
OL,5,Cmurals
OL,7,FTottenham Hotspur has become the first
OL,8,FEnglish football club to add audio
OL,9,Fdescriptions to its murals.
OL,11,FThe artworks of Son Heung-min, Harry
OL,12,FKane and Ledley King outside Spurs
OL,13,FStadium now include audio descriptions
OL,14,Ffor visually impaired fans.
OL,16,FPeople can scan a QR code to hear
OL,17,Fabout the murals. It's part of a
OL,18,Fcollaboration with visual impairment
OL,19,Fcharity the David Katz Foundation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
