PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772644277
OL,3,CSpurs becomes first English football
OL,4,Cclub to add audio descriptions to
OL,5,Cmurals
OL,7,FMarc Silver, CEO & Founder of
OL,8,FMurWalls, said: "Being part of the
OL,9,FDavid Katz Foundation (DKF) from its
OL,10,Finception has been a genuine
OL,11,Fprivilege. This project is about more
OL,12,Fthan murals - it's about access,
OL,13,Fempowerment and inclusion.
OL,15,FThrough MurWalls, we were honoured to
OL,16,Fcelebrate Harry, Sonny and Ledley for
OL,17,FTottenham Hotspur and its incredible
OL,18,Fsupporters.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1772644277
OL,3,CSpurs becomes first English football
OL,4,Cclub to add audio descriptions to
OL,5,Cmurals
OL,7,F"As co-founder and trustee of DKF, I'm
OL,8,Feven prouder that we've helped bring
OL,9,Fthe audio description to life,
OL,10,Fensuring visually impaired fans can
OL,11,Fexperience the artwork just as
OL,12,Fpowerfully as everyone else."
OL,14,FMatt Collings-Winter, Co-Chair of
OL,15,FSpursAbility, Tottenham Hotspur's
OL,16,FDisabled Supporters Association,
OL,17,Fadded: "We are thrilled that the club
OL,18,Fhave elevated these three iconic
OL,19,Fmurals to the next level while
OL,20,Fensuring inclusivity not only for our
OL,21,Fmembers but for the wider community.
